    "Preliminary materialsThis discussion begins by defining key terms crucial for understanding the topics explored in this article.",
    "These concepts form the bedrock of the ideas presented herein, and a detailed explanation of each follows in subsequent sections.",
    "Autonomous vehicleWe should first emphasize that the driver behavior monitoring systems have been used in human-driving vehicles for a long time, for instance, by insurance companies through mobile apps or small hardware equipment.",
    "However, these systems are more critical for autonomous vehicles as well as vehicles that utilize advanced driver-assistance systems, i.e., using a level of autonomy, because they may face unpredictable situations requiring the driver's intervention.An autonomous vehicle with any levels of autonomy revolves around a vehicle that can operate without (or with minimum) human intervention.",
    "These vehicles are designed to navigate and drive themselves, relying on advanced technologies and systems rather than requiring a human driver."
